r: rgb(204, 204, 221);\"><br></span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Verdana, Arial\" size=\"2\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(204, 204, 221);\">#fear</span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Verdana, Arial\" size=\"2\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(204, 204, 221);\"><br></span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></div>',0,'2014-01-21 14:28:34'),(14,52,'Dirty. Noisy. Screaming. Shouting. Strange smells. Blurry shapes moving, making strange noises. A lack of air. Coughing. Dragons through the window.<div><br></div><div>Darkness.</div>',0,'2014-01-21 14:30:51'),(15,52,'aww fuck, this is bright.... I preferred being in the dark, this is just a bitch for the eyes. Oh wait, I dont have to have them opened, sweeeet. But it\'s freaking cold here, and dry. I don\'t like it. Why can\'t I just go back in there? I guess I\'ll get in to one of those another day. WOOOA whats going on now? My chest is like swelling or something I hope I won\'t explode :O oh ok now it\'s shrinking again... it never did this while I was chilling in there. MEEEH this swelling and shrinking is exhausting I hope it\'ll stop doing that soon.&nbsp;<div>Hmm I feel an urge emerging... I want to shoot people? what does that mean? and what is that I\'m holding in my hand? some kind of weird stick that makes loud noises like \"BANG\" weird... I guess it\'s in my genes or something.&nbsp;</div><div>Wait why am I making random incoherent noises like these? This makes no sense. Wait now I remember how to talk properly GAAAA GAAGAGAGGAAAAA GAAA WUOOOÄÄÄÄÄÄ!</div>',0,'2014-01-21 14:31:35'),(16,52,'<p>Wow, what is this? I felt a strange feeling on my skin. I see blurring objects and everything is cold around me. I\'m scared I thought I was going to die. So I screamed, I screamed as hard as possible thinking that it would save me. </p><p>Suddenly, I hear voices. I was sure that something\'s getting closer to me and I\'m going to die. Then I felt a warm embrace. I don\'t know what it is but from that moment I know I felt safe.</p>',0,'2014-01-21 14:31:38'),(17,52,'The light is so bright, it\'s blinding. This must be the reason why such a large people amount of people have impaired eyesight. I swear I\'ll sue this hospital when I\'m older and make them pay for my eye laser surgery when I\'m forty. &nbsp;I can already see myself being one of those smart-looking toddlers wearing gigantic, colourful glasses that cover half of my face. Ugh, breathing seems also to be an issue. My god, I\'ll probably have to walk around with an asthma inhalator all of my life. Well at least I\'ll have a legit excuse to miss out on the horrible PE lessons I will most likely have to attend. And Oh lord... My skin, it\'s all purple. I must have some kind of eczema. A tub of skin lotion will have to follow me everywhere I go... &nbsp;And OH LORD are those my PARENTS!? Let me guess, they live in a cramped apartment in the suburbs and own un ugly Volvo probably filled to the brim with baby things awaiting my arrival. They\'re probably so excited, they think I will save their miserable, failing marriage. Yeah right, I\'m just going to make things worse. But oh look at their faces... they looked so chocked! Don\'t say they thought I was going to be a girl... and that... the whole rear of the car is filled with PINK baby toys!! My god, my past life was so much better. Ugh.&nbsp;',0,'2014-01-21 14:37:00'),(18,52,'AAAAAAAAAH MY EYES ARE ON FIRE. Close them, quick! Phew. Okay. Nice and dark again. Why is there no air in here- I\'m supposed to open my mouth to breathe now? We didn\'t have these kinds of issues back in the dark place I came from... breathe in, breathe out? And I just keep doing that? What a lot of work... didn\'t have to do that in the womb. Wait, what\'s that sound? Oh, that\'s me screaming. Sounds good. Nice and clear. HEY. What\'s holding me? Okay, I\'m opening my eyes again. Just to see what it is. Ugh, blinded... wait, I can see things! Holy baloney, what is that thing, a cyborg? Let go of me, weird dude! What exactly are the scissors- WOAH. NOT COOL, MAN, NOT COOL! That cord connected me to my mom and everything! It\'s, like, symbolic. Get off me. Who are you handing me to? What do you think I am, some common object? We didn\'t have objectification in the womb... plus it was dark in there and you didn\'t get manhandled. Hey, don\'t give me to someone else, come on, man... why is this woman crying? Why is she putting her mouth on my head... woah. Don\'t eat me, crazy lady! Wait... that\'s my Mom? Oh. Uh, hi. Why are you opening your mouth again? What do you mean, you\'re naming me Göran? I\'m going to kick you to show my displeasure. Is there a return policy for babies? Return me. I want to go back to the dark place.&nbsp;',0,'2014-01-21 14:37:04'),(19,52,'Hell yeah! After 9 insanely long months I\'m crawling! I\'m crawling out of my mothers womb for gods sake! Is there anything like this, and will there ever be? I don\'t want this feeling to end, ever!<div><br></div><div>Oh shit! There\'s a this wall! No one mentioned this wall. Not even my mother told me it while stroking me through her skin, who\'s now screaming random noises. It seems easier to here what she says when I\'m not turning my ass towards the wall, so I better spin around to face the wall.</div><div><br></div><div>Wait! It seems there\'s this super tiny opening exposing light. The light is bright! Is this it? Is this the end? Even though this might be, this is pretty worth it. It really is the ride of my life and I better walk the line. It seems I can push the tiny opening and make it bigger!</div><div><br></div><div>Oh my lord! I\'m out somewhere! I think I see myself from outside and have the greatest out of body experience ever!</div><div><br></div><div>I\'m on the other side of life!</div>',0,'2014-01-21 14:39:51'),(20,52,'I woke up in chock. I felt something wet around my neck. Something was pushing my head from all sides. It was a pain I had never experienced. After what felt like an eternity I could see a bright ceiling. People were standing all around me. Starring. Laughing. Some were even crying. I didn\'t remember how I ended up there. I didn\'t even know where I was. I could see my sister starring at me from outside the room. I tried to call her name but she didn\'t react. I asked what was going on. No one answered. They just stared at me. They looked happy. \"It\'s a boy!\" they shouted. I shouted right back at them. Asking what the hell was going on. No one answered. They just shushed me.',0,'2014-01-21 14:40:27'),(21,52,'Dirty. Noisy. Screaming. Shouting. Strange smells. Blurry shapes moving, making strange noises. A lack of air. Coughing. Dragons through the window.<div><br></div><div>Darkness.</div>',0,'2014-01-21 14:40:30'),(22,52,'I would like to build a new computer.<div><br></div>',0,'2014-01-21 14:40:30'),(23,52,'Wow shieet... what did i just do? <br><br>I just wanted to try something new!&nbsp;<br>The universe can\'t just open up? I just got this strange urge to turn my self upside down and explore the periphery of the universe... but all of a sudden the brightest of lights emergen and a giant hand grab my head.<div><br></div><div>The hand, which size were about ten times of mine, started to pull me, as to punish me for my vicious curiosity. Oh creature from the light, forgive my defiance, I surely didn\'t intend to intrude on your domains.<br><br>God please help me on this road to hell and be merciful in your punishments.</div><div><br><br></div>',0,'2014-01-21 14:40:43'),(24,52,'<p class=\"perspective gender\" style=\"font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">Hello.</p><p class=\"perspective gender\" style=\"font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\"><i>Hello.</i></span></p>',0